Swimming Pool Design.

Desjoyaux offers a team of highly skilled and experienced pool manufacturers and installers, specialising in the design, construction, and installation of custom designed luxury pools. With over 50 years of expertise, our teams are dedicated to delivering exceptional pools tailored to our clients needs. Based on your individual requirements, our pool designers and installers turn your vision into reality

Pool Design

Pool Safety Covers.

Slatted security pool covers, not only help retain the heat within your pool but add security to secure your swimming pool.  Whether it is a new pool or an existing pool, our wide range of pool covers will meet your technical constraints, your budget and your desires. Our covers, from basic to advanced, are custom-made to protect your pool, offering a variety of options and finishes.

Automatic pool covers

Swimming Pool Heating.

Air-source heating provides 80% of the heat generated into your pool free of charge; independently certified efficiency. Our swimming pool heat pump systems are amongst the most efficient and low-cost swimming pool heating systems on the market. Our range of Polytropic heat pumps will enable you to enjoy your pool to the full from the very first rays of spring sunshine right through to the very end of the season. Backed up with remote monitoring management and app control via 4G connectivity.
